&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;This benchmark does not include any relic. You may bench 2k higher with the proper relic equipped.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;
&lt;small&gt;Alternative relics include &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;100916&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;Â Relic of the Thief and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;99997&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;Â Relic of Isgarren.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;
